Disgusted with the purge and the blind obedience to <span style="color: #8B0000;">Stalin</span>, a significant number of <span style="color: #700000;">**KPD**</span> members and voters are abandoning the party. These disillusioned workers, seeing no other home on the left, are now cautiously looking towards the <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span>. While their support is welcome, it brings with it a new wave of radicalism that will be difficult to manage. The <span style="color: #700000;">**KPD**</span>, meanwhile, has become an even more unpredictable and hostile force.
  
